    <item>
      <title>中国誓言支持经济增长，铜价再次突破 10,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/base-metals-edge-lower-as-doubts-swirl-over-china-s-stimulus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国高层领导人加大刺激经济增长力度的带动下，铜价自 7 月份以来首次回升至每吨 10,000 美元，其他工业金属价格也出现上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/base-metals-edge-lower-as-doubts-swirl-over-china-s-stimulus</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 03:30:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特和利比亚有望增加石油供应，油价继续大幅下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-26</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据报道，沙特阿拉伯承诺在 12 月份增加产量，而利比亚各派达成协议，可能为恢复部分原油生产铺平道路，导致油价连续第二天下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-26</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 23:30:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
